name: Farm Flight: Adventures of a Bird, Bee and Sheep
name_original: Farm Flight: Adventures of a Bird, Bee and Sheep
description:
Are you up for the challenge? Navigate the farm animals as they fly through the obstacles. Try to go as far as you can! Choose from a chicken, bee, or sheep each with their own unique flight abilities.

-Go as far as you can to get the highest score
-Play as different animals each with their own flight characteristics
-Compete against the world!
